Participant Management includes these new metadata types to generate research study randomization blocks and to randomly assign candidates to research study comparison groups.

New Metadata Types in Life Sciences Cloud

Generate research study randomization block records
Use the generateResearchStudyBlocks value in the existing actionType field, which is on the FlowActionCall subtype on the Flow metadata type.
Randomly assign candidates to research study comparison groups
Use the assignCndtToResearchStudyGroup value in the existing actionType field, which is on the FlowActionCall subtype on the Flow metadata type.
